<!-- 定義與症狀 -->
'''腹主動脈瘤'''（{{lang-en|abdominal aortic aneurysm, AAA}}<ref name="loganabbrev">{{cite book|author1 = Logan, Carolynn M.|author2 = Rice, M. Katherine|title = Logan's Medical and Scientific Abbreviations|url = https://archive.org/details/logansmedicalsci00loga|date = 1987|publisher = {{le|J. B. Lippincott Company}}|location = Philadelphia|isbn = 0-397-54589-4|page = [https://archive.org/details/logansmedicalsci00loga/page/3 3]|ref = logansaabrev}}</ref>），為{{Link-en|腹主動脈|Abdominal aorta}}局部[[血管舒張|擴大]]，其橫徑大於3公分或超過正常橫徑之50％<ref name=Kent2014>{{cite journal | author = Kent KC | title = Clinical practice. Abdominal aortic aneurysms. | url = https://archive.org/details/sim_new-england-journal-of-medicine_2014-11-27_371_22/page/2101 | journal = The New England Journal of Medicine | volume = 371 | issue = 22 | pages = 2101-8 | date = 27 November 2014 | pmid = 25427112 | doi=10.1056/NEJMcp1401430}}</ref>。除非腹主動脈瘤破裂，否則通常無症狀<ref name=Kent2014 />。偶爾造成腹部、背部、腿部等處[[疼痛|疼痛]]<ref name=AFP2006>{{cite journal | author = Upchurch GR, Schaub TA | title = Abdominal aortic aneurysm | journal = Am Fam Physician | volume = 73 | issue = 7 | pages = 1198–204 | year = 2006 | pmid = 16623206 }}</ref>，較大的腹主動脈瘤，有時甚至可藉由腹部觸診感覺到搏動。破裂時可能造成腹部或背部[[疼痛|疼痛]]、[[低血壓|低血壓]]、或[[昏厥|短暫失去意識]]<ref name=Kent2014 /><ref name=Spa2014>{{cite journal | author = Spangler R, Van Pham T, Khoujah D, Martinez JP | title = Abdominal emergencies in the geriatric patient. | journal = International journal of emergency medicine | volume = 7 | pages = 43 | date = 2014 | pmid = 25635203 | doi=10.1186/preaccept-3303381914150346 | issue=1}}</ref>。

<!-- 病因及診斷 -->
腹主動脈瘤大部份發生在50歲以上，尤其男性以及具有家族史的病患<ref name=Kent2014 />。其他危險因子包括[[吸菸|抽煙]]、[[高血壓|高血壓]]、以及[[心血管疾病|心血管疾病]]<ref>{{cite journal | author = Wittels K | title = Aortic emergencies. | journal = Emergency medicine clinics of North America | volume = 29 | issue = 4 | pages = 789–800, vii | date = November 2011 | pmid = 22040707 | doi=10.1016/j.emc.2011.09.015}}</ref>。基因方面如[[馬凡氏症候群|馬凡氏症候群]]及[[埃勒斯-當洛二氏症候群|橡皮人症候群]]，可能增加罹病風險。腹[[主動脈瘤|主動脈瘤]]為最常見的動脈瘤<ref name=CDC2014>{{cite web|title=Aortic Aneurysm Fact Sheet|url=http://www.cdc.gov/dhdsp/data_statistics/fact_sheets/fs_aortic_aneurysm.htm|website=cdc.gov|accessdate=3 February 2015|date=July 22, 2014|archive-date=2017-05-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170502131503/https://www.cdc.gov/dhdsp/data_statistics/fact_sheets/fs_aortic_aneurysm.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>，大約85%位在腎臟以下的主動脈，其餘則在[[腎|腎臟]]同高或以上的位置<ref name=Kent2014 />。在美國，建議65歲至75歲且抽煙的男性，接受[[超音波|超音波]][[疾病篩檢|篩檢]]<ref name=pmid15989299>{{cite journal | author = Cinà CS, Devereaux PJ | title = Review: population-based screening for abdominal aortic aneurysm reduces cause-specific mortality in older men | journal = ACP J. Club | volume = 143 | issue = 1 | page = 11 | year = 2005 | pmid = 15989299 | url = http://www.acpjc.org/Content/143/1/issue/ACPJC-2005-143-1-011.htm | access-date = 2015-04-12 | archive-date = 2016-03-03 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160303171838/http://www.acpjc.org/Content/143/1/issue/ACPJC-2005-143-1-011.htm | dead-url = no }}</ref>。在英國，則建議所有65歲以上男性應接受篩檢<ref name=Kent2014 />。澳洲則沒有篩檢準則。一旦發現腹主動脈瘤後，需要定期作超音波檢查<ref>{{cite journal|last1=Robinson|first1=D|last2=Mees|first2=B|last3=Verhagen|first3=H|last4=Chuen|first4=J|title=Aortic aneurysms - screening, surveillance and referral.|journal=Australian family physician|date=June 2013|volume=42|issue=6|pages=364-9|pmid=23781541}}</ref>。

戒菸或不吸菸為預防此疾病的最佳方法。其他則包含治療[[高血壓|高血壓]]、減少[[高膽固醇|高膽固醇]]的現象、避免[[超重|體重過重]]。當腹主動脈瘤橫徑，在男性超過5.5公分，在女性超過5公分，則建議接受手術<ref name=Kent2014 />。其他修補手術的適應症包括有症狀及大小快速增加<ref name=AFP2006 />。修補可藉由{{Link-en|開腹手術|Open aortic surgery}}或{{Link-en|血管內動脈瘤修補|Endovascular aneurysm repair}}<ref name=Kent2014 />。比起開腹手術，血管內動脈瘤修補雖然有以下好處：短期內死亡風險較低、住院時間較短；但必要時仍需要接受開腹手術<ref name=Kent2014 /><ref>{{cite journal | author = Thomas DM, Hulten EA, Ellis ST, Anderson DM, Anderson N, McRae F, Malik JA, Villines TC, Slim AM | title = Open versus Endovascular Repair of Abdominal Aortic Aneurysm in the Elective and Emergent Setting in a Pooled Population of 37,781 Patients: A Systematic Review and Meta-Analysis. | journal = ISRN cardiology | volume = 2014 | pages = 149243 | date = 2014 | pmid = 25006502 | doi=10.1155/2014/149243}}</ref><ref>{{cite journal | author = Biancari F, Catania A, D'Andrea V | title = Elective endovascular vs. open repair for abdominal aortic aneurysm in patients aged 80 years and older: systematic review and meta-analysis. | journal = European journal of vascular and endovascular surgery : the official journal of the European Society for Vascular Surgery | volume = 42 | issue = 5 | pages = 571–6 | date = November 2011 | pmid = 21820922 | doi=10.1016/j.ejvs.2011.07.011}}</ref>。長期來看，兩者的預後情況沒有很大的差別<ref>{{cite journal | author = Paravastu SC, Jayarajasingam R, Cottam R, Palfreyman SJ, Michaels JA, Thomas SM | title = Endovascular repair of abdominal aortic aneurysm. | journal = The Cochrane database of systematic reviews | volume = 1 | pages = CD004178 | date = 23 January 2014 | pmid = 24453068 | doi=10.1002/14651858.CD004178.pub2}}</ref>，除了EVAR可能要重覆開刀的可能性較高<ref>{{cite journal | author = Ilyas S, Shaida N, Thakor AS, Winterbottom A, Cousins C | title = Endovascular aneurysm repair (EVAR) follow-up imaging: the assessment and treatment of common postoperative complications. | journal = Clinical radiology | volume = 70 | issue = 2 | pages = 183–196 | date = February 2015 | pmid = 25443774 | doi=10.1016/j.crad.2014.09.010}}</ref>。

<!-- 預後及流行病學-->
腹主動脈瘤影響約2%至8%的65歲以上男性，而男性的疾病發生率是女性的四倍。若動脈瘤橫徑小於5.5公分，隔年的破裂風險小於1%；橫徑在5.5至7公分之間者，則為10%；大於7公分更高達33%。破裂後的死亡率是85%至90%<ref name=Kent2014 />。1990年，腹主動脈瘤造成10萬人死亡，而在2013年，更造成15萬2千人死亡。在2009年的美國，腹主動脈瘤則造成1萬至1萬8千人死亡<ref name=CDC2014 />。

